<CDLItem itemNbr="56-21-01" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.CDL.3-56-21-01.1.3-56-21-01">
<Title>Passenger Window Seals</Title>
<DispatchCondition>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>Any or all window seals may be migrated.The seals may migrate to protrude in the airflow, but are not permitted to be missing from the window frame assembly.</Para>
<Para>A migrated window seal will generally be visible in a walk-around inspection without the need to measure actual seal displacement.</Para>
<Para>Utilize the equations provided in Table 1 and Table 2 below to calculate the appropriate penalty for 15 or more migrated window seals. For under 15 migrated window seals, the table penalty must be applied.</Para>
<Para>Consult AMM 56-21-01 to determine if noted seal mismatch indicates seal migration.</Para>
